# {{name}}

An AI agent powered by Claude and Castari.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Deploy to Castari
cast deploy

# Invoke the agent
cast invoke {{name}} "Hello!"
```

## Local Development

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Run locally (test with stdin)
echo "Hello!" | npm run dev
```

## Customization

- Edit `src/index.ts` to customize agent behavior
- Edit `CLAUDE.md` to change agent instructions
- Add secrets with `cast secrets set {{name}} KEY value`

